'''''Health Promotion Practice''''' is a bimonthly [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[healthcare journal]] that covers research in the field of [[public health]], especially the practical application of health promotion and education. The [[editor-in-chief]] is Leonard Jack, Jr. ([[Xavier University of Louisiana]]). It was established in 2000 and is currently published by [[SAGE Publications]] on behalf of the [[Society for Public Health Education]].

== Abstracting and indexing ==
''Health Promotion Practice'' is abstracted and indexed in:
* [[CINAHL]]
* [[Index Medicus]]
* [[MEDLINE]]
* NISC{{clarify|date=January 2012}}
* [[PsycINFO]]

